text: Cathy Grainger-Brain is a retired judoka from Australia. Cathy competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. She was born on September 20, 1967.Cathy Grainger-Brain == References == Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Olympians for Australia Category:Australian judoka Category:Sportspeople from Canberra
